<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 yǒu nǐ wǒ jiù yǒu liàng guāng yǒu nǐ wǒ jiù yǒu fāng xiàng
 zài dà hǎi zhōng nǐ gěi wǒ kāi dào lù nǐ shì wǒ de bì fēng gǎng
 wǒ yào jǔ mù xiàng nǐ yǎng wàng nǐ yǒng yuǎn shì wǒ de lì liàng
 zài shā mò zhōng nǐ gěi wǒ kāi jiāng hé wǒ de líng a zài xiàng nǐ gē chàng</lyrics>
<title>yǒu nǐ wǒ jiù yǒu liàng guāng 迦南579</title>
</song>